    "attributes": {
        "action": "Remove a week from the school summer holiday to extend the Easter holiday",
        "additional_details": "We think this would mean that:\r\n \r\n1. Children can spend more quality time with family during Easter time.\r\n2. Local businesses can benefit after dry winter spell.\r\n3. Parents can take longer holidays during Easter time.",
        "background": "We think the Government should require schools to add 1 additional week to the existing 2 week-long holiday at Easter, and remove 1 week holiday from the holiday in July - September.",
